      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of July 23 Economic View column on estate tax; New Zealand no long collects an estate tax upon death (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The Economic View column last Sunday about alternatives to an estate tax misstated New Zealand's tax treatment of wealth transfers. The country has a gift tax; it no longer collects an estate tax upon death.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>The Economic View column last Sunday about alternatives to an estate tax misstated New Zealand's tax treatment of wealth transfers. The country has a gift tax; it no longer collects an estate tax upon death.</p>
